** Argo Checkers - Remake of a classic!  **
** From Software Creations & Argo Games. **
 Gorgeous graphics, great sound, and smooth
play make this the most enjoyable Checkers
game ever! Includes over a MEG of animated
256 color VGA graphics & digital sound. 
From the makers of HEXXAGON.
Req: VGA, 286 or above. SB support. <ASP>
